Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,Dialogue,Credits,0,0,0,,Subtitle-source: Detective Conan - 194 [KnKF][9B96FE12].avi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:12.72,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song: Mystery Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:12.72,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by: Garnet Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no shape to flowing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no figure to flowing winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what the case, the deductions are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The melody lingering in her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brought upon a strange investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child but the brains of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.54,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Because you and I are two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:27.54,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,kimi to boku to ha betsu no ikimono dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:36.75,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,konomi ga chigau aruku hayasa mo omoi no tsutae kata mo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:36.75,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Hobbies, walking speed nor the way we\Ncommunicate, our thoughts are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.02,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,iroaseteyuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:39.02,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Times{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:44.09,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Amongst the memories of the two, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:44.09,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,futari no kioku no naka ima bokura ha
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.29,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Though troublesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.29,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tesaguri dakedo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:51.23,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Ever searching for someone else and the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:51.23,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,hoka no dareka wo mirai wo sagashite yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.50,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Living stronger than once thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.50,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,omou yori tsuyoku ikite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.17,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Seeking a special love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.17,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tokubetsu na ai motometeru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.37,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,shikana hibi ni nayandari
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.37,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Getting confused in the tough days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:05.68,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,True heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.68,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,True heart for mystery eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:09.65,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Don't let go of that hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:09.65,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,mou nido do mayowanai you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:13.22,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,So that you won't get lost once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:13.22,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,sono ude wo hanasanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.05,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Even we hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.05,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,kizutsuke au sono toki mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:24.00,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Just keep searching for the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:24.00,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tada zutto kotae wo sagashite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:27.63,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,mayoi konda toki no naka de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:27.63,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,During the times we get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.40,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,To the next place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.40,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,tsugi no basho he
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:33.97,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,you take your way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:33.97,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,You take your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:38.14,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:38.14,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:45.68,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:45.68,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,I feel so all in secret life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, who stumbled onto a case and was wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Managed to recover thanks to Ran donating her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran knew about my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, with the antidote Haibara made,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I returned to Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with Haibara disguised as Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's suspicions had disappeared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, let it subside again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's... She's waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... Can't return to Conan yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha-Haibara... You... Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,24 minutes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess this is within the permitted range.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll return this to you, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:57.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:57.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box. (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apotoxin 4869's antidote.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't say never, but I can't give it to a deducting\Nmaniac who can't hold himself back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll try to stop myself from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, that was only a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't use an underdeveloped medicine for extended periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, there is a real possibility that you may die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess with only Paikaru's ingredients,\Na full antidote can't be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at least not without the drug's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just be thankful that your identity wasn't revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I knew something like this would happen,\NI would've told Ran what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you sure you're not going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Haido Avenue's indoor pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are really cool waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I still have a small cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something good must've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They served curry at school today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not like you, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were pretty excited about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.78,Dialogue Top,Sign,0,0,0,,Mouri Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess this means I have to restart from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah man, it's already summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.26,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs23}Note: Spring symbolizes a period of joy and relief from one's troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like spring will come anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.93,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs23}Translation Note: "Haru yo Koi" means "Come Dear Spring."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This song is... "Haru yo Koi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have a son as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's just a little freeloader that we're looking after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this music box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some areas seem to have notes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How old are you young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm around 7, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's only in first grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he always notices little things,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That become the hints to solving cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? A little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, should we tell Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll find something that would lead us\Nto the person Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person she's looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.49,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs23}Bell buddies are friends that contact each other via pagers,\Nkind of like instant messenger programs now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bell buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person you're looking for is a bell buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:57.44,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yuuki Haruna (21)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:57.44,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Fine Arts Major University Student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I met him 3 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:58.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,When I became a fine arts student at the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt lonely because I couldn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I just randomly entered a number\Non my pocket bell and sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My name is Haruna,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be my friend?" I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then to my surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a response saying "My first love\Nwas also Haruna. Nice to meet you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since, we've been bell buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was like a kind uncle who would listen to your every concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you sent "I wish to see you," in your\Npocket bell, then wouldn't he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have his pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was getting harder and harder to pay\Ntuition while I was attending school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought about seeing him before I quit school and went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to arrange a meeting with Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nin front of Shibuya station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no matter how long I waited, I didn't see anyone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was about to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I looked inside, this music box\Nwas in it along with his pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know that was his pocket bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a message on that pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This is a very valuable music box."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Use it to pay for your schooling and don't\Ngive up on your dreams, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't accept such valuable merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe if I got the music box examined,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might be able to find its owner and return it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I took it to an antique shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the person at the store only said\Nit was a broken, old, music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, weird messages have been sent to my pocket bell lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I have something to ask you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Come to the location I tell you now, alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was different from the messages\NI received from Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got scared, so I didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, other messages were sent later that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "Cat Burglar!" more than 10 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over 10 times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Cat Burglar?" Do you have any ideas as to why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I want to ask what the person's intentions\Nare, but I have no way to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it might have something to\Ndo with Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, so I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that message is still coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it continued for some time, but it has stopped now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means our only lead is this music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:09:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what we can get from a music\Nbox that is missing a few notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the broken pins on the drum of the music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like they were old and broke off on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rather they were forcefully removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's some sort of message!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the music is "Come, Dear Spring," and the missing\Nnotes are near the end, "Ra, Do, and Ra."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Radora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a monster you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know the lyrics to the missing notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lyrics are "onnmo e-he detai to matte iru," so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The missing ones are "Mo "De" and "Ru".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mo De Ru... Model!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who had that was a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, now that we know that, we can\Nsearch the model companies for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be faster if we just go meet the person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, we can't do that, so we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket bell number, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is tell officer Takagi the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then ask him to ask the pocket bell company,\Nand you'll at least find out his address.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found out the address and the phone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might have more potential than Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was because of Officer Takagi that we got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just a misuse of authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you sure\Nthey said we can go to their house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, even though the one who answered\Nthe phone wasn't Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that everyone in his family\Nknew that he was into pocket bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told them that I wish to return\Nhis pocket bell and music box,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They replied, "Please come!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be exciting to find out who Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:06.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Kazuko (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:06.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Female Head of the Ogata Family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You weren't coming alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh, we're just tagging along... I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk about that later, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:13.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The rumoured Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue Top}-san{\r} has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.99,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Shirou (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.99,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Second Son of the Ogata Family
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have her rest in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was, after all, the pillar of Grandpa's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess we should put up some incense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Incense...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he died at the end of last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By any{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce, was Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about this music box you say you received from my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it was a very valuable music\Nbox, so I would like to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...? This music...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, Dear Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:18.42,Dialogue Top,Note,0,0,0,,{\fs23}Note: The Japanese koto is a large string instrument, about\Nsix feet long. It is traditionally played on the floor. And it originated\Nin China but, came to Japan in the 7th-8th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the music that Mother always played on Koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:16.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Tsuneo (53)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:16.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kazuko's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would Mother be the woman in that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:25.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the woman next to Father is my mother,\NHaruna, who died 3 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa probably thought of you as Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was very happy, saying: "Haruna came back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, excuse my rudeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have a pocket bell at that age, he really is a unique individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, ever since Mother died, Father began\Nto take walks late into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we gave him one in case of emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, was there anything inside the music box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know... Like... Maybe a...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stamp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:15.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A stamp from a group of four, worth about 200 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:15.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ogata Minoru (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:15.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,First Son of the Ogata Family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you came all the way to this house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because the old man told you where\Nit is and you came to find it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll reveal your true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, get very comfortable, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, please don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His company isn't doing very well, so he's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you came all this way, please stay for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would like to hear more about you and Father's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this about a 200 million yen stamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what do the missing notes in that music box mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Question after question after question during dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make it worse, it started to rain and it isn't letting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, other than this family's second born,\NShirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, everyone else is a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the back of Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s memoir stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day he died was December 6th.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing strange about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said she received the music box last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means if we believe what Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the one who gave Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the music box\Nwas someone other than Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's forget about the bad things and get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An old man with a cane just went left down that hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I saw it go left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only room to the left is ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my daughter says she saw a weird shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was just their imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the guest that slept\Nover last time said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They thought someone went by their pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like this happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there should only be us in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he taking a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded like a wire on an instrument was cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the room with Mother's koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi... Minoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru... Hey Minoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This message...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:22.85,Dialogue Top,Sign,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then could that shadow of an old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this message be from the deceased Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once a person dies, he can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have time to say stupid things, go call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-This might be a murder...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't consider me dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got hit on the head with something hard all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By something hard, you mean that koto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the koto that Grandma treasured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't... Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you who hit me, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because when the loud sound came,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone was together in Ran-neechan's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who? Didn't you see the culprit's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, your wound is on your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that you were hit from the front, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was too dark to see any faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means when you were hit, this room was dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by the time I noticed anything strange, it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so strange about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what were you doing alone in a dark room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:18:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably felt a presence in this room and came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when he was about to turn the light\Non, someone hit him with the koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about the message sent\Nto Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket bell, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was probably Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably had an appointment with a friend tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she had completely forgotten about it and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning, that message was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From her friend who wanted to say "I've\Nbeen waiting for you for a while."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong, Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't remember making a promise like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot has happened today, so I suppose anyone would forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about the shadow of the old man I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the person who attacked my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for an elderly man with a cane to hit a person\Nwith that heavy koto and knock him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly, even if that elderly man existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is probably impossible for him to knock out Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran says that elderly man disappeared just down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he wanted to run into the room\Nin the back, Conan and I were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That elderly man was most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the old saying, "The true identity\Nof a ghost is just a dead tree."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought you saw a ghost because\Nyou're always so afraid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, Madam, please call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like someone other than us was in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was someone hiding here like Uncle said?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, what is that person's objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the looks of things, it doesn't look\Nlike it's been searched through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it was a crime committed\Nspecifically against Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this isn't Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a good idea why Minoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in this dark room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how and when did the culprit know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the koto that was used as the weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there a reason behind the culprit\Nusing the koto as the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, there's so many things I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of an old man that Ran saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that really just Ran's imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That music box with the missing notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That music box must be hiding an important secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The location of the hidden object that the\Npeople of this house are looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 200 million yen stamp that Shuugo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:42.87,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Donna kotoba ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:42.87,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,How can I{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge my words,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:50.48,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,so that you may understand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:50.48,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Kimi ni tsutaerareru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:59.56,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Since then numerous seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:59.56,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,arekara ikutsumo no kisetsu ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:05.73,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,have passed by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:05.73,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,toorisugita keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:12.97,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,But you always smiled beside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:12.97,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,itsumo soba de waratteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:23.58,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,watashi nimo ienai koto ga mada hitotsu dake aru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:23.58,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Even I still have one thing I cannot say
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:25.68,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Secret Of My Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:25.68,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Secret Of My Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.49,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,utagattemo nai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.49,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I hold no suspicions
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:34.49,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,itsu datte sukoshi no mirai ga areba
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:34.49,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Always as long as there is a little future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:39.43,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,shinjitsu wa te ni irerareru hazu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:39.43,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I should be able to find the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.00,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,I can't say mou sukoshi dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:43.00,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I can't say, Just a little more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:46.17,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for a{\rHonorifics - Dialogue Top} chan{\r}ce
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:46.17,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for a{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:24:15.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Next Conan Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this sharp for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the key signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Key signature?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I received the music box last Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be, father died on December 6th last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it the doings of a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Co-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:21.61,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:21.61,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Poignant Music Box (Part2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Electric Fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.54,0:24:31.62,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Wait in excited anticipation for the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.91,0:24:28.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time is my dreaded music{\rHonorifics - Dialogue Top} tan{\r}gle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.55,0:24:30.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Secret of my heart!
